g.text: US$ change in gov’t health spend per capita per +$1 external (lagged 1 year)
Dot = effect of +$1 external pc (t−1) on change in government health spend pc (t) | Whiskers = 95% CI
Model per country: ΔGov_pc ~ lag(External_pc). Points filled=significant (p<0.05); open=not significant. Source: WHO GHED.
